name: TheOne
description: As a found footage artist I always dreamt about finding actual footage on the street. On September the third 2013 exactly 8 years ago I found this piece of film on the corner of Sülzburgstr./Emmastr. in Cologne. It's been in a moving box almost the entire time. I have no idea why it looks the way it looks and what happened to it and to whom it belongs. In no way had I had any artistic input in its outcome. I only scanned it. And now I will sell this scan on this platform. It's TheOne I found and I never knew what to do with it. So this evening I will return it where I found it.
